service-checker (0.2.1-1) stretch-wikimedia; urgency=medium

  * Allow skipping cert verification
  * Drop trusty support
  * Drop python2, python 3.4 support
  * Add python3.7 (which is in Debian Buster) support
  * Fix various debianization issues

